quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,73,"Àwa ṣe iná ayé ní ìrántí (fún Iná ọ̀run) àti n̄ǹkan èlò fún àwọn onírìn-àjò."
  56,74,"Nítorí náà, ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún orúkọ Olúwa rẹ, Atóbi."
  56,75,"Nítorí náà, Mò ń fi àwọn àyè tí ìkọ̀ọ̀kan gbólóhùn al-Ƙur’ān wà nínú sánmọ̀ búra.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[“Mọwāƙi‘u-nnujūm” tún lè túmọ̀ sí “àwọn ibùsọ̀ ìràwọ̀ nínú sánmọ̀”. Nítorí náà, ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn fún āyah yìí nìyí: “Nítorí náà, Mò ń fi àwọn ibùsọ̀ ìràwọ̀ búra.” Ẹ wo sūrah an-Najm;  53:1 àti ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ rẹ̀.]
  67,13,"Ẹ wí ọ̀rọ̀ yín ní jẹ́ẹ́jẹ́ tàbí ẹ wí i sókè, dájúdájú Òun ni Onímọ̀ nípa ohun tó wà nínú àwọn igbá-àyà ẹ̀dá."
  67,14,"Ṣé kò mọ Ẹni tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá ni?Òun sì ni Aláàánú, Alámọ̀tán. {1}",footnotes:1:[Ìtúmọ̀ méjì ló wà fún āyah yìí nínú àwọn tírà Tafsīr. Ìtúmọ̀ kìíní: “Ṣé kò mọ Ẹni tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá ni?” Ìyẹn ni pé, “Ṣé ẹ̀dá kò mọ Ẹlẹ́dàá rẹ̀ ni?” Ìyẹn ni pé, tí ẹ̀dá bá lérò pé, bí òun bá sọ̀rọ̀ ní ìkọ̀kọ̀, ó yẹ kí ẹ̀dá náà mọ̀ dájú pé, nínú ìròyìn Ẹlẹ́dàá rẹ̀ ni pé, Ẹlẹ́dàá nímọ̀ èrò-ọkàn àwọn ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀, áḿbọ̀sìbọ́sí ọ̀rọ̀ tí àwọn ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀ sọ ní ìkọ̀kọ̀.]
  67,15,"Òun ni Ẹni tí Ó rọ ilẹ̀ fún yín. Nítorí náà, ẹ rìn ní àwọn agbègbè rẹ̀ káàkiri, kí ẹ sì jẹ nínú arísìkí Rẹ̀. Ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀ sì ni àjíǹde ẹ̀dá wà."
  68,7,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Ó nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ẹni tó ṣìnà kúrò lójú ọ̀nà Rẹ̀. Ó sì nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa àwọn olùmọ̀nà."
  68,8,"Nítorí náà, má ṣe tẹ̀lé àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́."
  68,9,"Àti pé wọ́n fẹ́ kí o dẹwọ́, kí àwọn náà sì dẹwọ́."
  69,4,"Àwọn ìjọ Thamūd àti ìjọ ‘Ād pe Àjíǹde (ajámọláya bí àrá) ní irọ́.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Nínú àwọn orúkọ fún Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde ni Ìṣẹ̀lẹ̀ Òdodo náà àti Ajámọláyà bí àrá.]
  69,5,"Ní ti ìjọ Thamūd, wọ́n fi igbe tó tayọ ẹnu-ààlà pa wọ́n rẹ́."
  69,6,"Ní ti ìjọ ‘Ād, wọ́n fi atẹ́gùn líle tó tayọ ẹnu-ààlà pa wọ́n rẹ́."